    "Name": "Ronin",
    "Details": "The SA-RN7 is built on an endo steel chassis, and is powered by a 250 XL engine that allows the 'Mech to move up to 86.4 km/h. Protection is provided by nine and a half tons of ferro-fibrous armor. The main armament is the large pulse laser and a pair of LRM-10 launchers fed by two tons of ammunition. These are backed up by a single ER small laser, a claw, and two M-Pods. The 'Mech's waste heat is managed by the standard 10 double heat sinks.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Protected Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
